  "slug": "rotom-phone-cobblemon",
  "title": "Rotom Phone Cobblemon",
  "description": "This mod add the Rotom Phone to be used in Cobblemon",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Rotom Phone is a Forge and Fabric mod for Cobblemon.</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Rotom Phone is a useful item that allows you to use your PC and Healing anywhere, saving you from having to carry them in your inventory. It also has its own Chest to store items and also allows you to use CheckSpawn.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjJhcfl3JuCAxXmqpUCHbu9BccQ3ewLegQIBhAQ\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1127734171196981268/1207188862510571550/2024-02-14_01.49.05.png?ex=6631cbbd&amp;is=661f56bd&amp;hm=2cabc3fa520d7c34628f465e117f09384404cc914cfe397e12a496056b9790a0&amp;\" alt=\"GuiRotomTelefone\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1070\" /></span></strong></span></p>\n<p id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjW_Km_xK6EAxUejpUCHZndBsQQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\">Installation Requirements</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjW_Km_xK6EAxUejpUCHZndBsQQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Rotom Phone only works with <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cobblemon\">Cobblemon</a>.</span><strong><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"><br /></span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\">Rotom Phone Chest</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjW_Km_xK6EAxUejpUCHZndBsQQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The Rotom Phone Chest has 63 storage spaces and has the same function of storing items as the Ender Chest.</span><strong><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"><br /></span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1127734171196981268/1207188863009824848/2024-02-14_01.49.41.png?ex=6622a27d&amp;is=662150fd&amp;hm=2e34c6c35f89a5abdc2759adf725e530ba6228ae44346754fd241afd22605641&amp;=&amp;format=webp&amp;quality=lossless&amp;width=1202&amp;height=676\" alt=\"GuiChest\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1070\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjW_Km_xK6EAxUejpUCHZndBsQQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\">Recipe</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjW_Km_xK6EAxUejpUCHZndBsQQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You can create a Rotom Phone with 6 copper ingots, 2 glass panels and a diamond.</span><strong><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"><br /></span></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong style=\"text-align: right; font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1127734171196981268/1207188863886430258/2024-02-14_01.51.16.png?ex=6631cbbd&amp;is=661f56bd&amp;hm=3fb902113d9cc35f95f32daf4c26c4be3a56c5a91019a52cd3f9a2a15258a91a&amp;=&amp;format=webp&amp;quality=lossless&amp;width=1202&amp;height=676\" alt=\"ReceitaRotomPhone\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1070\" /></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Rotom Phone CheckSpawn</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwiSuIDYra6EAxX6lZUCHbqXAWoQ3ewLegQIARAU\"><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Rotom Phone CheckSpawn allows you to see which Pok&eacute;mon appear in the biome you are in and shows a % chance of each Pok&eacute;mon appearing.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1127734171196981268/1207188863437508648/2024-02-14_01.50.01.png?ex=6631cbbd&amp;is=661f56bd&amp;hm=712b5fa7c398b064a3ae7ab6289bc5bdd9c601cbbce29cc28e9fe680fe26d064&amp;=&amp;format=webp&amp;quality=lossless&amp;width=1202&amp;height=676\" alt=\"GuiCheckSpawn\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1070\" /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Modpacks</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjW_Km_xK6EAxUejpUCHZndBsQQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Yes, you can use this mod in your Modpack.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjW_Km_xK6EAxUejpUCHZndBsQQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\">Sponsor</span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tradu&ccedil;&atilde;o\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwjW_Km_xK6EAxUejpUCHZndBsQQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This project is sponsored by BisectHosting. If you're looking for a server, <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/\">check out their hosting plans</a> and use promo code <strong>Mur1lu</strong> at checkout to get 25% off your first month!</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\" style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1102457697040863307/1179546629150359663/1701296191235.jpg?ex=6632bf67&amp;is=66204a67&amp;hm=4af23d0a80006de3710f3649990ec8c7ac0ddfa232046627971826e6d4ea5774&amp;\" alt=\"BisectHosting-Mur1lu\" width=\"1903\" height=\"550\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Author</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a title=\"MUR1LU\" href=\"https://twitter.com/mur1lu\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">MUR1LU</span></span></span></span></a></span></li>\n</ul>",
